WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.480
Well, good morning, family.

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:03.960
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:05.793
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:05.793 --> 00:00:09.480
It's not morning, but almost.

00:00:10.806 --> 00:00:33.680
It's pretty late at night, but I just wanted to come on and pray with you all a little bit tonight before you all go to bed, praying over your week that you will have a victorious week, that this week will be a week of breakthrough for your household, and that we're closing out 2025 not broke, busted, and disgusted, but believing God for the overflow.

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:39.617
You know, I told you all, make that list and stretch your faith.

00:00:39.617 --> 00:00:41.280
You need spiritual stretch marks.

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:51.080
I've talked about it how many times now—that you are believing God so big, but you're so pregnant spiritually that you have spiritual stretch marks.

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:56.775
It's time to believe God for the exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:00:56.775 --> 00:01:02.080
That's where I said, "Let's finish 2025 with the overflow.

00:01:02.462 --> 00:01:13.396
" When the Lord is showing us in the vision to believe for your house to be paid off, believe for your student loans, believe for your car note to be paid off, and to be debt-free.

00:01:14.449 --> 00:01:20.940
We have about eight weeks left of this year, and it's nothing for God.

00:01:20.940 --> 00:01:27.497
I just know He can turn it on a dime, and there's a million and one ways that He can get you a million dollars.

00:01:27.497 --> 00:01:28.800
I just believe it.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:30.589
And you say, "Well, Brandon, why are you saying all that?

00:01:30.589 --> 00:01:37.596
" Because He's been stretching me to believe Him for bigger and to have spiritual stretch marks.

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:46.800
If you don't have spiritual stretch marks, you're not believing big enough because you're not pregnant enough with what God has called you to do.

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:53.200
You're not stretching out there knowing that God is able to do it.

00:01:53.200 --> 00:02:00.055
If you're just barely believing, that's where you're going to be; you're just going to barely get by and barely hit the status quo.

00:02:00.055 --> 00:02:08.240
But if you're believing for big, I would rather believe for huge and get half of it than believe for small and get nothing.

00:02:09.912 --> 00:02:21.720
Believe for an overflow so big that you go, "Man, I'm not only believing for my house to be paid off, but I'm going to pay off my pastor's house.

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:23.560
" Why not believe big?

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:31.156
I've got so much overflow to have my stuff paid off that I've got enough to pay off three other people's stuff.

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:45.445
I'm a lender unto many, and I shall not borrow.

00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:55.080
Why not believe for big?

00:02:55.080 --> 00:03:03.262
So, I set out to believe for big things for the rest of the year going into 2026.

00:03:03.262 --> 00:03:06.000
What are you believing God for in 2026?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:15.239
I'm believing for my kids to be saved, I'm believing for my wife to be saved, and I'm believing for my husband to be saved.

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:19.740
I want to walk in the supernatural.

00:03:19.740 --> 00:03:20.530
Why not?

00:03:20.530 --> 00:03:21.430
Why not you?

00:03:21.430 --> 00:03:22.269
Why not me?

00:03:22.269 --> 00:03:24.040
There's an expiration date to your problems.

00:03:24.040 --> 00:03:25.617
That's where I was at today.

00:03:25.617 --> 00:03:34.800
Guys, I was blowing the leaves off in my yard and cleaning up my yard today because the leaves are falling so heavily now.

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:39.960
It's starting to rain leaves here in Tulsa, and the leaves are saying hello.

00:03:42.135 --> 00:03:48.352
I told Diana I don't like this part of the year whenever these leaves are doing all that, but it's a blessing, and we're so thankful for the trees.

00:03:48.905 --> 00:03:53.490
I just want to say that to you all just to stretch yourself to believe.

00:04:06.463 --> 00:04:06.777
When I was outside and I was doing the yard work, prayer tonight was at the church, and Pastor Candace and them always have prayer.

00:04:11.486 --> 00:04:11.714
I was like, "Man, I want to finish these leaves.

00:04:11.714 --> 00:04:15.680
" Then the Lord said, "Brandon, I want you to go to prayer and add your supply.

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:21.050
I want you to take your family, and I want you to add your supply.

00:04:21.050 --> 00:04:25.745
There's things that I'll show you in reward if you go.

00:04:25.745 --> 00:04:28.480
I want you to add your supply.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:31.440
" So I said, "Okay, Father.

00:04:31.440 --> 00:04:32.169
I'll do it.

00:04:42.834 --> 00:04:49.890
" I love prayer anyway; it's not like you have to twist my arm to go pray.

00:04:49.890 --> 00:05:02.590
But when you're busy and you're wanting to finish the job and there's a pile of leaves that you've blown, I thought, "Well, if the wind gets them, they get them.

00:05:02.590 --> 00:05:07.538
" But I put them in the pile and I told Diana, "Let's go, babe.

00:05:07.538 --> 00:05:11.024
" So we were a little late, but we went in.

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:25.191
I started praying, and the lady that was leading the prayer tonight was praying over families, for the Thanksgiving season, and for strife not to be in the homes—basically stuff like that.

00:05:25.191 --> 00:05:34.084
She said her prayer assignment today was praying over finances and stuff.

00:05:52.245 --> 00:05:52.610
I believe there's an anointing for that—to pray for certain things that God calls your vein of what you're to pray for.

00:05:52.610 --> 00:06:04.377
He shows me a lot about the economy privately that I don't talk about—about the housing market, about gold, about everything—and I just intercede for this.

00:06:17.020 --> 00:06:29.770
So I just started adding my supply, and all of a sudden I was taken in the spirit and saw what the spirit of God was showing me.

00:06:29.770 --> 00:06:31.840
I saw four major, huge doors.

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:40.629
They were built on a rock, but it wasn't a normal rock.

00:06:40.629 --> 00:06:46.347
It looked like a white, chalky rock, but it was holy.

00:06:46.347 --> 00:06:50.190
All these doors were built on this rock.

00:06:50.190 --> 00:06:55.296
I could see each individual one was completely black.

00:06:55.296 --> 00:07:02.580
Take your screen on your cell phone when it's turned off—that blackness.

00:07:03.893 --> 00:07:09.691
It looks like that; it's piercing, it swallows you, and you get lost in it.

00:07:09.691 --> 00:07:19.600
These doors were so black that you couldn't make out the door handles, but I knew they were separate and individually done.

00:07:19.820 --> 00:07:28.613
The Lord had me praying over these doors, and all of a sudden the middle door opened up, and in this door were golden coins.

00:07:28.613 --> 00:07:33.760
Megan's laughing about those golden coins; she gets excited; she's in the living room.

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:34.480
She's fine.

00:07:37.324 --> 00:07:42.960
The golden coins were on a hill, and as the door opened up, they started falling through the door like an avalanche.

00:07:43.490 --> 00:08:01.503
These were all stacked up really high, and as the door opened, it was so full of golden coins that they started coming out because the pressure was on the door.

00:08:01.503 --> 00:08:13.990
I was looking at that door, and the Lord said to pray, because it was so dark that the outside of it was hidden.

00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:19.960
You had to pray into it; you had to contend for it.

00:08:19.960 --> 00:08:25.240
Like I keep telling y'all, we have to contend for the blessing.

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:30.207
You cannot just idly sit by and expect to walk in the abundance for these last days.

00:08:30.207 --> 00:08:35.217
We know that Satan's wheelhouse, his specialty, is over finances.

00:08:35.217 --> 00:08:44.840
So we are going and plundering the demonic realm and saying, "Listen, we're taking back what you stole from us.

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:54.897
We're taking back everything the devil has stolen from us, and we're demanding the thief pay us double for our trouble.

00:08:54.897 --> 00:09:00.863
" I'm calling for double for my trouble—everything that you have been stealing from me for how many years.

00:09:00.863 --> 00:09:04.955
Then the Lord said, "Call for your ancestors' finances.

00:09:04.955 --> 00:09:06.910
" We were praying into this.

00:09:27.057 --> 00:09:27.389
I haven't even brought this up yet.

00:09:27.389 --> 00:09:32.156
But the Lord said to us, "Call for your ancestors' seeds, too.

00:09:33.470 --> 00:09:38.220
If your family generation worked hard, sowed, and were givers at their church but they never reaped it, he said, 'Call for their seeds, too.

00:09:38.220 --> 00:09:43.029
If they never reaped it, those seeds do not die.

00:09:43.029 --> 00:09:45.285
'" Seeds do not die.

00:09:45.285 --> 00:09:59.480
He said, "They lie dormant sometimes in the ground or, if they're in a dark place, they won't grow until the light hits them or unless water hits them.

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:08.640
You can put seed in there.

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:12.185
" He said, "Speak to those old seeds to reap a harvest, Brandon.

00:10:12.185 --> 00:10:23.834
For there's generational wealth that is coming for the body of Christ if you lay hold to it, for this last outpouring of finances, for an end-time harvest transfer.

00:10:23.834 --> 00:10:26.400
" Sister Billye said, "I didn't know if it was biblical or not.

00:10:26.400 --> 00:10:29.680
" She said that because you always want to know if you're off.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:34.080
If it's not in the Word, you cannot go against what the Word says.

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:40.302
So Sister Billye Brim, who wrote this book we were talking about yesterday that Diana read—she's an elder and I always respect my elders.

00:10:45.890 --> 00:10:46.085
She started researching all the biblical basis for an end-time wealth transfer and she says it's in the Word.

00:10:46.085 --> 00:10:46.720
She found it all.

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:53.200
She goes through the Greek; she's brilliant when it comes to this stuff.

00:10:53.650 --> 00:11:02.911
I love it when you can talk to her and have a really cool conversation about the Word; she's full of the Word.

00:11:05.013 --> 00:11:05.267
The end-time wealth transfer is there.

00:11:05.773 --> 00:11:19.180
As I was praying into this—and maybe we'll have her on one day and she can talk about it because you want to know where that's at in the Word—I'm not educated enough to tell you.

00:11:22.006 --> 00:11:28.415
I'm humble enough to tell you that I don't know, but I trust her and I'll allow her to come on and show you in the Word where it's at because I thought it was awesome.

00:11:28.415 --> 00:11:30.570
She had it all in there.

00:11:30.570 --> 00:11:37.170
Going back to the doors: I saw these four doors and as I was praying, the Lord said, "These are end-time.

00:11:37.170 --> 00:11:38.502
This is what's hidden.

00:11:38.502 --> 00:11:39.658
It's in the darkness.

00:11:39.658 --> 00:11:45.573
You have to pray and contend for it and bring it out into the light.

00:11:45.573 --> 00:12:00.560
" As you are praying, I saw the gold door open and all this coin, and then I saw silver open and the silver started to fall out.

00:12:12.839 --> 00:12:12.977
I said, "What are the other two doors?

00:12:30.900 --> 00:12:31.240
" I don't know yet.

00:12:44.215 --> 00:12:48.376
But as I was praying, the Lord was showing me—and this is not financial advice, I'm not telling you to buy silver or gold—I'm telling you what I saw behind the door and what I'm praying over.

00:12:49.024 --> 00:12:55.120
You pray too and ask God what He's telling you because I'm still trying to ask God what this is all about.

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:57.920
As I was praying, I saw these doors open.

00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:00.855
Then I saw two doors over here and they represented something.

00:13:00.855 --> 00:13:05.253
But as I was praying, I could see these four electric lines on an electric pole.

00:13:05.253 --> 00:13:11.827
What was interesting was the electric pole was blacked out so much that you could not really make out that it was an electric pole.

00:13:11.827 --> 00:13:19.839
The electric lines were like lines you see on the earth running to—I was trying to show them like a black extension cord—but they were like a black cord.

00:13:19.839 --> 00:13:21.440
It's all right, son.

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:26.011
It's a black cord that was running and powering each door.

00:13:28.657 --> 00:13:28.823
And the Lord said, "Flip the switch.

00:13:28.823 --> 00:13:29.765
Flip the switch.

00:13:29.765 --> 00:13:32.880
" I started interceding for this.

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:36.280
When I started seeing this black cord—thanks, Braden.

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:37.240
Black headphones.

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:40.004
You can have them back, buddy.

00:13:40.004 --> 00:13:40.738
Thank you.

00:13:40.738 --> 00:13:43.360
As I was praying, the Lord said, "Pray into this.

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:53.655
" I get these assignments and I'm like a boy.

00:13:53.655 --> 00:13:59.270
The lady up at the front is leading and going a totally different direction, but I'm in the back with my heels ground down in the ground.

00:13:59.270 --> 00:14:00.880
I'm like, "No, hold on.

00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:04.587
We have to park here because I want to see more.

00:14:04.587 --> 00:14:07.027
" I'm not leading, so I'm just trying to remember this.

00:14:07.027 --> 00:14:13.040
