00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:19.240
But I was on my own little hound trail—you know, like a bloodhound.

00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:29.260
Their noses are to the ground and they're going to find out what this is in the spirit realm.

00:14:29.260 --> 00:14:37.440
That's just the way I am because I am determined to have everything that God has for me.

00:14:37.440 --> 00:14:44.784
I am determined to make sure I don't lack any good thing for my family.

00:14:44.784 --> 00:14:51.466
