00:14:51.466 --> 00:14:58.360
We have what it takes to do it.

00:15:03.699 --> 00:15:04.079
We're contenders.

00:15:10.514 --> 00:15:12.949
The Lord told me on the way home, I told her, I said, "Do we do a live stream tonight?

00:15:12.949 --> 00:15:14.794
" because it was late already.

00:15:24.535 --> 00:15:24.750
I said, "You know, there are certain things I could have done, but let's pray some more about these doors.

00:15:24.750 --> 00:15:27.046
Let's go ahead and do a live stream.

00:15:27.046 --> 00:15:31.817
" I fed the kids and said, "Let's go and do the live stream.

00:15:35.913 --> 00:15:41.240
" As I was praying into this and Braden was getting this set up, the Lord said to me, "Brandon, I am assembling together the closers even more.

00:15:42.267 --> 00:15:45.269
