00:15:49.053 --> 00:15:54.760
You're the generation, I believe with all my heart, that will not taste death.

00:16:03.860 --> 00:16:04.145
We will be that generation that sees the Lord Jesus Christ come back for His church.

00:16:11.035 --> 00:16:15.434
But He brought us here for such a time as this, not just to sit by idly and watch the end-time unfold around us, but to pray into it and to have an assignment for angelic aid and assistance.

00:16:15.434 --> 00:16:22.640
We're not just sitting back idly and going, "Well, God, whatever will be will be, Que sera, sera.

00:16:22.640 --> 00:16:23.547
" No.

00:16:31.760 --> 00:16:32.297
The sky is not falling.

00:16:32.297 --> 00:16:35.890
