00:18:41.451 --> 00:18:56.080
" I hate to burst your bubble, but he's going to try to devour the ones who are hiding more than the ones who have a sword out saying, "You come over here and I'm going to slap you in the head with this.

00:18:56.080 --> 00:18:57.630
" Do you think he doesn't see that?

00:18:57.630 --> 00:18:58.480
He's attracted to fear.

00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:02.670
