00:20:02.307 --> 00:20:07.250
If we don't contend and stand for what we believe in, we'll lose it.

00:20:07.250 --> 00:20:11.926
' I'm telling you, the body of Christ is the salt of this earth.

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:26.050
And we are to do what it takes.

00:20:26.050 --> 00:20:28.315
