00:20:28.315 --> 00:20:30.235
I believe the Holy Spirit does.

00:20:30.235 --> 00:20:32.544
Christ in us, the hope of glory.

00:20:32.544 --> 00:20:35.747
Christ in you.

00:20:48.220 --> 00:20:48.560
We're the restrainers from the evil.

00:20:54.587 --> 00:21:01.180
