00:23:02.634 --> 00:23:25.514
Just because we have a limp-wristed gospel and a lot of people that don't want to tell you the truth that Jesus Christ is coming—and he's coming back for a glorious church without spot or wrinkle—doesn't mean that it's not going to happen because they're not telling you.

