00:24:29.340 --> 00:24:30.120
The British are coming!

00:24:30.120 --> 00:24:37.373
' I'm the Paul Revere of this generation, riding in the midnight hour, telling you that Jesus is coming.

00:24:39.100 --> 00:24:40.056
You need to get your house ready.

00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:46.190
You need to get your boat ready because as in the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:24:50.450 --> 00:24:51.100
And I'm telling you, look around you, folks.

00:24:51.100 --> 00:24:52.560
Look around you.

00:24:52.560 --> 00:24:56.027
Wars and rumors of wars, plagues and pestilences, earthquakes in divers places.

00:24:56.027 --> 00:24:57.830
We had one in the Philippines today.

00:24:57.830 --> 00:25:02.429
We had one in Afghanistan today.

00:25:02.429 --> 00:25:04.980
In divers places, we're having these earthquakes.

00:25:04.980 --> 00:25:13.080
And many people are so desensitized to all of it because we hear about it all the time that you think it's just the status quo.

00:25:13.080 --> 00:25:32.447
And as a frog in a pot, as the water keeps getting hotter and hotter and you don't even realize that you're getting boiled alive, you must realize where we are and the signs of the times and the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:25:32.447 --> 00:25:41.211
It's time to fall on our face before a holy God and say, 'God, have mercy on this generation.

00:25:41.211 --> 00:25:45.119
' We need a harvest of souls like we've never seen before.

00:25:45.119 --> 00:25:47.355
We need a revival.

00:25:47.355 --> 00:26:08.759
We think, 'Well, Charlie Kirk went home and we have a couple of months,' and like I told you, you all go back into your lackadaisical ways—'Well, you know, the holidays are coming, so we're focused on that'—until we have another major event and it shakes you a little bit and you go, 'Well, that shouldn't have happened.

00:26:08.759 --> 00:26:16.160
' Brother Hagin said anything that happens in this earth that is bad is a church prayer failure.

00:26:16.160 --> 00:26:17.555
It's a church prayer failure.

00:26:17.555 --> 00:26:25.600
And that's why the Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, it's going to take much prayer in these last days.

00:26:25.600 --> 00:26:31.120
So raise up a million men and women prayer army.

00:26:31.120 --> 00:26:33.835
Come on the internet and pray with my people.

00:26:33.835 --> 00:26:35.160
Teach them to pray.

00:26:35.160 --> 00:26:41.389
Teach them to have fellowship with me and tell them that I'm coming.

00:26:41.389 --> 00:26:44.189
' I said, 'Lord, they know you're coming.

00:26:44.189 --> 00:26:46.760
' Most of the church knows.

00:26:58.120 --> 00:26:58.309
Well, the ones I hang around, at least we all talk about it all the time.

00:26:58.309 --> 00:27:07.690
He looked me straight in the eyes and he said, 'Brandon, they don't know.

00:27:07.690 --> 00:27:09.070
They don't know.

00:27:09.070 --> 00:27:10.024
There's no urgency.

00:27:10.024 --> 00:27:11.080
There's no urgency in my church.

00:27:11.080 --> 00:27:16.000
For I'm going to create an urgency for one last call.

00:27:18.115 --> 00:27:18.280
I'm going to shake this generation one more time.

00:27:19.337 --> 00:27:26.029
And I'm going to bring them to their knees for fearful sights they will see that will bring them to their knees.

00:27:26.029 --> 00:27:40.747
' And there will be five major shakings throughout this earth: a shaking in politics, a shaking in finances, a shaking in the earth's crust and earthquakes, a shaking in the heavens, and a shaking in the church.

00:27:40.747 --> 00:27:41.980
Five major shakings.

00:27:41.980 --> 00:27:53.460
You're going to see, and we're seeing some of it right now, but as I'm telling you, as labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:07.760
I'm telling you, we're going to see.

00:28:08.985 --> 00:28:17.480
He even told us even the day, he said, 'Watch from the 23rd of September, for September will be a month to remember.

00:28:17.480 --> 00:28:22.844
' And Charlie Kirk went home.

00:28:22.844 --> 00:28:26.089
September will be a month to remember.

00:28:26.089 --> 00:28:27.227
Nobody will forget it.

00:28:29.851 --> 00:28:31.616
And I'll never forget what happened with Charlie Kirk.

00:28:31.616 --> 00:28:32.672
Never.

00:28:32.672 --> 00:28:37.673
But I saw major revival coming to college campuses.

00:28:37.673 --> 00:28:44.679
I saw a major revival coming throughout this earth.

00:28:44.679 --> 00:28:47.856
I saw brush arbor churches.

00:28:47.856 --> 00:28:53.720
I saw churches that were on fire.

00:29:15.586 --> 00:29:16.013
I saw the pastors preaching repentance.

00:29:16.013 --> 00:29:23.920
But then he said, 'Be patient with my babies for they're coming.

00:29:23.920 --> 00:29:26.720
They're coming in hot, Braden.

00:29:26.720 --> 00:29:31.504
' And so I just keep trying to tell you and sounding the alarm over and over.

00:29:34.120 --> 00:29:38.160
And you say, 'Well, Braden, I've already heard this,' but you need to hear it again.

00:29:42.218 --> 00:29:42.613
You need to hear it again.

00:29:42.613 --> 00:29:48.140
You need to have that fan flamed to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:29:55.624 --> 00:29:57.629
And I'll keep doing this.

00:29:57.629 --> 00:30:08.120
Just like Jeremiah kept warning the people that stuff was coming and they kept saying, 'Oh, we heard that.

00:30:08.120 --> 00:30:16.216
' How many times did you read him saying the same thing over and over and over again to the point it seemed redundant?

00:30:26.822 --> 00:30:27.093
But he said it to the point where it happened.

00:30:37.211 --> 00:30:37.589
And I'm telling you, life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:30:43.410 --> 00:30:43.765
And I'm telling you, you need to watch what you say.

00:30:43.765 --> 00:30:51.760
I told D, I said, 'We've got to come up higher in our confession.

00:30:51.760 --> 00:31:01.809
We've got to come up higher in what we're saying because life and death is in the power of the tongue.

00:31:01.809 --> 00:31:05.407
But as a man thinketh in his heart, so is he.

00:31:05.407 --> 00:31:10.893
But as you think, what you speak, out of the abundance of the heart, the mouth speaks.

00:31:25.280 --> 00:31:25.591
And what you're saying is what you're living today.

00:31:25.591 --> 00:31:29.236
What you said yesterday is what you're going to live.

00:31:29.236 --> 00:31:34.810
What you said today is what you live tomorrow or the next day.

00:31:34.810 --> 00:31:40.830
But what you keep saying out of your mouth because your tongue...

00:31:41.220 --> 00:31:46.373
the Bible says the tongue is the pen of a ready writer.

00:31:46.373 --> 00:31:50.538
I believe your tongue is the pen of a ready writer.

00:31:50.538 --> 00:31:51.960
You're writing your ticket.

00:31:51.960 --> 00:31:54.165
You're writing what you're living.

00:31:54.165 --> 00:31:58.344
' What are you saying out of your mouth?

00:31:58.344 --> 00:32:01.200
What are you believing?

00:32:01.200 --> 00:32:02.955
'My marriage is terrible.

00:32:02.955 --> 00:32:06.280
My kids are all rebellious.

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:07.880
' You have what you say.

00:32:07.880 --> 00:32:08.573
'Well, we're poor.

00:32:08.573 --> 00:32:09.440
We'll always be poor.

00:32:09.440 --> 00:32:10.469
Grandma was poor.

00:32:10.469 --> 00:32:12.120
Her great-grandma was poor.

00:32:15.840 --> 00:32:16.342
You know what?

00:32:16.342 --> 00:32:28.851
We're always just going to be some backwoods people that just kind of live off the land.

00:32:28.851 --> 00:32:32.200
' No, I'm more than a conqueror.

00:32:32.200 --> 00:32:34.587
I have more than enough.

00:32:34.587 --> 00:32:37.208
My bank account is in overflow.

00:32:37.208 --> 00:32:40.904
I'm just going to say that I'm not moved by what I see.

00:32:40.904 --> 00:32:42.920
I'm not moved by what I feel.

00:32:42.920 --> 00:32:45.679
Even when you click the bank account and you look at it, I'm not moved by you.

00:32:52.145 --> 00:32:52.450
I speak to you to change.

00:32:54.897 --> 00:32:55.103
It may say you're in the negative.

00:32:55.103 --> 00:33:00.665
You're looking at it and saying, 'I don't care what you say.

00:33:12.103 --> 00:33:12.469
I believe that my God is an abundant supply.

00:33:12.469 --> 00:33:15.100
He supplies all my needs.

00:33:15.100 --> 00:33:20.700
' The doctor comes and gives you a bad report.

00:33:20.700 --> 00:33:23.777
The doctor says you have four weeks to live.

00:33:31.960 --> 00:33:32.389
I speak to this report.

00:33:33.674 --> 00:33:35.209
I refuse to believe this.

00:33:35.209 --> 00:33:41.620
Even if you go down fighting, at least you stood for something good.

00:33:41.620 --> 00:33:51.425
Whether you are absent from the body and present with the Lord, either way you win, but at least you believe God for it all the way.

00:33:51.425 --> 00:33:53.166
Whose report will you believe?

00:34:04.390 --> 00:34:04.580
We shall believe the report of the Lord.

00:34:08.695 --> 00:34:09.771
I believe you're going to have to believe in this day and in the days ahead.

00:34:09.771 --> 00:34:12.620
You're going to have to contend.

00:34:12.620 --> 00:34:16.745
I'm telling you this because I see a storm coming.

00:34:16.745 --> 00:34:18.613
People don't want to hear it.

00:34:18.613 --> 00:34:24.867
'Well, you know, you're looking into the tribulation, brother.

00:34:24.867 --> 00:34:28.257
' No, I'm seeing labor pains.

00:34:31.920 --> 00:34:32.380
I'm seeing storms.

00:34:32.380 --> 00:34:33.890
I'm seeing a plague again.

00:34:58.058 --> 00:34:58.320
I saw it again today.

00:34:58.1000 --> 00:35:01.182
I have a glimpse into it.

00:35:11.270 --> 00:35:11.475
The Lord shows me and I am praying.

00:35:11.475 --> 00:35:15.968
I see the plague and I'm looking at people dying.

00:35:15.968 --> 00:35:22.880
Today I'm outside blowing my leaves off and I see it and I go, 'What am I supposed to do with that?

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:30.880
