00:40:38.480 --> 00:40:52.407
We see the darkness, but we have authority.

00:40:52.407 --> 00:41:06.040
We're praying and we're bringing down this assignment from the enemy.

00:41:06.040 --> 00:41:23.880
I'm telling you folks, many hands make light work.

00:41:23.880 --> 00:41:35.000
I've said enough; it's been 30 minutes.

00:41:56.640 --> 00:42:02.015
I tried to keep it under 30 minutes tonight because I told Diana, 'I'm talking way too long.

00:42:02.015 --> 00:42:28.427
' I just wanted to try to stir you up a little bit before we pray that you have authority, and that's why we do this.

00:42:28.427 --> 00:42:37.340
We're going to pray, and if the Lord shows me more about these doors, great.

00:42:37.340 --> 00:42:42.640
If He doesn't, He'll show me some other time.

00:42:42.640 --> 00:42:58.686
But I know that we are in a time of something supernatural about to take place for the Body of Christ as we enter into this month of November.

00:42:58.686 --> 00:43:15.794
I believe it's going to be a time of great acceleration for us—not sitting back and saying, 'What a missed opportunity.

