00:44:25.820 --> 00:44:38.990
From the top of my head to the soles of my feet, the Holy Spirit dwells within me.

00:44:39.000 --> 00:44:43.709
I am in overflow with the Holy Spirit.

00:44:43.709 --> 00:44:56.400
I thank You, Father, that You dwell on the inside of me, my wife, and my children.

00:44:56.400 --> 00:45:04.700
We receive it richly by faith—that we will lack no good thing, that we will lack no good gift.

00:45:04.700 --> 00:45:11.195
We will walk in the abundance of the Holy Ghost and fire in our household.

