Father, I thank You for Your body that was broken.

00:45:21.897 --> 00:45:22.526
You were beaten.

00:45:22.840 --> 00:45:28.137
You took it all on the cross.

00:45:28.137 --> 00:45:32.368
They whipped You with that cat-o'-nine-tails, Father.

