You did it for us.

00:46:18.120 --> 00:46:28.880
You became sin, You became sickness, You became poor, You became mentally disturbed.

00:46:28.880 --> 00:46:30.251
He took it all.

00:46:30.251 --> 00:46:40.000
He took that crown of thorns on His head.

