It says in His Word in 2 Timothy 1:7 that God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind.

00:46:56.040 --> 00:47:11.568
Because of what You did on that cross for us, we have a sound mind, because He became all that for us.

00:47:11.568 --> 00:47:22.833
So, Father, I thank You that we don't have to take it because in Galatians, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:47:22.833 --> 00:47:29.180
Because You took it on the cross, Father, we're redeemed from the curse.

00:47:29.180 --> 00:47:31.560
I'm not under the curse.

00:47:31.560 --> 00:47:33.500
Jesus has set me free.

00:47:37.862 --> 00:47:38.191
For sickness, I have health; for poverty, wealth; for Christ has ransomed me.

00:47:41.960 --> 00:47:48.827
We believe everything that You did for us, and we receive it in Jesus' name.

00:47:49.707 --> 00:47:50.000
Thank You, Lord.

00:47:50.000 --> 00:47:57.217
Thank You, Father, for all that You provided for us.

00:47:57.217 --> 00:47:58.886
Amen and amen.

00:47:58.886 --> 00:48:03.427
Take it; we don't have to be sick.

00:48:03.427 --> 00:48:06.280
