00:48:22.312 --> 00:48:29.040
We thank You, Lord, that no weapon formed against us is going to prosper.

00:48:29.040 --> 00:48:35.160
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

00:48:35.160 --> 00:48:39.137
We plead the blood of Jesus over us.

00:48:39.137 --> 00:48:46.573
We thank You, Lord, for the angels that are watching over us.

00:48:46.573 --> 00:48:58.865
If there's anything You want to show me or show her, Father, I thank You that we're willing and able to hear You, God.

00:48:59.180 --> 00:49:02.300
A stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:49:02.300 --> 00:49:14.486
Father, we thank You that we don't add to any prophetic confusion in the airwaves; we only hear You, Father, and we only see what You want us to see.

00:49:14.486 --> 00:49:18.040
We plead the blood over us in Jesus' name.

00:49:18.040 --> 00:49:20.600
Thank You, Lord.

00:49:20.600 --> 00:49:22.336
See, every time is different.

00:49:36.420 --> 00:49:36.670
It's just out of the flow.

00:49:50.863 --> 00:49:51.211
You want some of this?

00:49:54.451 --> 00:49:55.343
I usually don't drink this because it makes you burp.

00:49:55.343 --> 00:49:57.620
So, Father, here we go.

00:49:57.620 --> 00:49:59.383
Who wants to go tubing?

00:49:59.383 --> 00:50:04.160
Braden, you're so funny every time, baby.

00:50:04.160 --> 00:50:13.680
We're going to go tubing.

00:50:13.680 --> 00:50:17.129
We'll go down that Holy Ghost river.

00:50:17.129 --> 00:50:20.175
Let's pray together and see what the Lord has for us tonight.

00:50:20.600 --> 00:50:21.560
I feel there's something.

00:50:21.560 --> 00:50:24.909
Father, where you lead, we follow.

00:50:24.909 --> 00:50:28.131
Help us, Father, to go into those major rivers.

00:50:28.131 --> 00:51:04.846
Father, I thank you, Lord, for the Holy Ghost river of prayer, that we don't pray out of the flesh like that whiny prayer, but we pray out of the Holy Ghost and fire, and He prays through us, and we hit the target: spirit-led prayer.

00:51:04.846 --> 00:51:06.540
So we just thank you, Lord.

00:51:06.540 --> 00:51:07.080
We worship you.

00:51:07.080 --> 00:51:08.090
Oh, how He loves us.

00:51:08.090 --> 00:51:09.740
Oh, how He loves me.

