I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

00:53:42.840 --> 00:53:48.120
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

00:53:48.120 --> 00:53:51.493
I believe in miracles; I've seen a soul set free.

00:53:51.493 --> 00:53:54.707
Miraculous, the changing one redeemed through Calvary.

00:53:54.707 --> 00:53:57.560
I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

00:53:57.560 --> 00:54:01.140
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

00:54:01.140 --> 00:54:04.516
Father, we worship you and we believe in miracles.

00:54:29.491 --> 00:54:29.720
We believe in signs and wonders.

00:54:38.434 --> 00:54:38.646
We believe, Father, that you are the same yesterday, today, and forever.

